descriptionHtml:
Meet Freyja Wyvrngard (a replica of my character)
she is a female Nord, there are 2 diffrent save points one is when she has to search for armor and weapon before the starting dungeon,
the second file is right after the starting dungeon with all the loots I can find, and some ingredients (she ate some to find out each effect)
